What you need to know:

The 2020 FIFA Club World Cup was initially slated for December 2020, but was pushed to February 2021 due to the Covid-19 pandemic. Semi-finals are slated for February 7, while the third-place playoff and final will take place on February 11.Hosts Qatar said 12, 000 fans will be allowed into the stadiums during the Club World Cup (30 percent of capacity of stadium). Â 